text: Doris Emmie Grimes (1 January 1909 - 27 June 1987) was a British diver. She competed in the women's 10 metre platform event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1909 births Category:1987 deaths Category:British female divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:People from Wandsworth
